        it may be helpful to arrange the vertices of <m>A</m> as shown in <xref ref="fig_dirgraph3">Figure</xref>.
        <me>
          R = \{ (x, y) \in A \times A \mid x \text{ divides }  y \}, \qquad T = \{ (x, y) \in A \times A \mid x + y \text{ is even }  \}
        </me>.
      </p>
      <figure xml:id="fig_dirgraph3">
        <caption>Vertices for <m>A</m></caption>
        <image width="73%" source="images/figps-sec71-dirgraph.png"/>
      </figure>
    </investigation>
